lead_paragraph: Nairo Quintana protected his lead in the Tour of Catalonia through the sixth stage, won by Davide Cimolai, who sprinted ahead of the peloton to get the first win of the season for his Lampre-Merida team

headline.main: Nairo Quintana Protects Lead in Catalonia

snippet: Nairo Quintana protected his lead in the Tour of Catalonia through the sixth stage, won by Davide Cimolai, who sprinted ahead of the peloton to get the first win of the season for his Lampre-Merida team
abstract: Davide Cimolai wins sixth stage of Tour of Catalonia bicycle race; Nairo Quintana retains overall lead.
